N:npm-git-install
D:Install npm packages directly from GitHub repositories using git URLs. Use when installing packag...
G:npm git github install package-management
U[6]:
  **Packages Not on npm**: Install packages not yet published
  **Specific Branch/Tag**: Install main, develop, specific release tags
